## Test 36: payout 350.5 G fractional -> 350 G (rounded down)

What scenario yields fractional payout? Dragon-material item with damage that, divided by something... wait, only the 50% high-ench clause produces halves. Damage of an odd amount × 0.5 = .5. So e.g. high-ench (ench >=8) sword, damage 901 → 450.5, then 450.5 - 100 = 350.5. Round down → 350. ✓
